org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM diary_entries INNER JOIN users ON users.id = diary_entries.user_id LEFT OUTER JOIN languages ON languages.code = diary_entries.language_code WHERE users.status IN ("$1", "$2") AND diary_entries.visible = "$3" LIMIT "$4" OFFSET "$5"
